flowRoot.flowPara: You'll always need to be able to split signals and feed the same signal to different modules. This is a 1 to 8 un-buffered multiple, mechanically connected in a pretty smart way using switching jacks. It can be used as: 1 x 1 -> 8, 2 x 1 -> 4, 1 -> 5 & 1 -> 3, 4 x 1 -> 2, and so on... It's un-buffered with all the pros and cons that comes with un-buffered connections between multiple modules...
